summary: This is an email from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York regarding the transmission of a new discovery production for Ghislaine Maxwell. The email includes cover letters and indicates the materials were sent via FedEx.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell

events.title: Discovery Production for Maxwell
events.description: The U.S. Attorney's Office sends a new disc containing discovery materials for Ghislaine Maxwell via FedEx.

locations: 1 St. Andrew's Plaza, New York, NY 10007
keyFacts: On December 17, 2020, the U.S. Attorney's Office transmitted a new discovery production for Ghislaine Maxwell.
The materials were sent via FedEx and included cover letters.
The correspondence originated from the Southern District of New York at 1 St. Andrew's Plaza.
